Title: Better column width layout for availability reports with more groups
Level: 1
Edition: cee
Component: reporting
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.7i4
Date: 1450779445
Class: feature

When you create a report containing an availability table and that table has
more than one group then the column widths of each group would be different.
This was not very beautiful. Now all numeric columns get a minimum width und
thus the layout will be the same for all groups.
